entries.s_faf0f6d6: We've recently established ourselves in this new marketplace . Isn't it great? Sean Trenwell used his own money to help build it.
entries.s_f319b246: Our little market is tucked away in the city, but provides wonderful rewards for brave acts. I think some of the merchants here are looking for rare bones. Not sure where you'd get them from. But someone mentioned Sand People. Does that mean anything to you?
entries.s_e61c91fe: Actually, my Jawa friend may have something like that. Wait here a second while I discuss it with him.
entries.s_de2e386f: That's nice. I have to go.
entries.s_ce0e0612: Nice doing... well, we didn't exactly do business, did we. Thanks for coming by, I suppose.
entries.s_cb056ffb: Do you have record of that?
entries.s_c8e9e99a: Hi again. Good to see you... and oh, since you still have that disk I gave you, my friend thinks he can use something like that in an invention of his. But I guess you still need it, don't you. Nevermind.
entries.s_c1035c83: Ah, well return when you've done so.
entries.s_b4164d7b: Oh yeah? We'd love to help! Of course, we'll give it to you for the sake of helping Sean Trenwell win the election. Here you are. Good luck!
entries.s_a4149441: Let me tell you the situation...
entries.s_a1a4c8c9: Oh yeah? We'd love to help! Of course, we'll give it to you--Wait a second. Unfortunately, you don't have enough room. Come back when you do.
entries.s_9e71b2ab: In fact, he does. You're lucky you came today. He was going to take the disk apart and recycle it to make one of his new, crazy inventions. Why do you need it?
entries.s_7ffa475: Are you here to collect these influx capacitors? *pauses listening to the Jawa next to her* Oh... sorry, you're not the right person. While I've got your ear, I should let you knoww there's an election going on at the capitol. I encourage you to support Sean Trenwell if you get involved.
entries.s_40977666: Welcome! Oh, I remember you. Do you have enough room now to receive the evidence?
entries.s_1b885620: You didn't have enough room again. Come back when you do.
entries.s_14d1042b: Here you are. Good luck on the voting!
